PrecisOrder which (a) provides approval for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to make deductions from the final payments to producers of Soft White Spring wheat grown in Alberta for the explicit purpose of plant breeding research, and (b) designates the WESTERN GRAIN RESEARCH FOUNDATION as the "research funding agency".
Attachments
precis:
Order which (a) provides approval for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to make
deductions from the final payments to producers of Soft White Spring wheat
grown in Alberta for the explicit purpose of plant breeding research, and
(b) designates the WESTERN GRAIN RESEARCH FOUNDATION as the "research
funding agency".
